{"tid":724533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今年七一遊行人數可望止跌回升","createTime":"2018-07-01T03:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T12:35:20.000Z","uid":162272,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"14498f27b6ccc41fc533827a3d47560e5f62e4b1","tid":724533,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T03:58:27.000Z","msg":"今年天公造美放晴無雨， 加上大會呼籲遊行人士由更廣闊的東角道插隊，人數可望止跌回升。<br />\n<br />\n往年數字：<br />\n<br />\n民陣公布2017年遊行人數，稱有逾六萬人參加遊行。<br />\n<br />\n警方則指高峰期為一萬四千五百人，這是自從○三年有七一遊行以來最低。<br />\n<br />\n警方的遊行數字與港大社會工作及社會行政學系教授葉兆輝的統計小組推算相若，該統計小組推算為一萬五千至一萬七千人左右。<br />\n<br />\n港大民意研究計劃推算，七一遊行總人數介乎2.7萬至3.5萬之間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/113510_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F113510_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0b98cbc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c1251667a71f31fbcbf8225810fac0d820e22e7","tid":724533,"uid":22624,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:02:44.000Z","msg":"行禮如儀"},{"pid":"fc598cfc143837109c4191532edab2bc7379e188","tid":724533,"uid":38651,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:16:49.000Z","msg":"14年個年真係最勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲怨氣大到"},{"pid":"dd49f14f472933b0d827dc6095bc3540fbddf4e0","tid":724533,"uid":139251,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:22:15.000Z","msg":"大家都死左心 香港人攰喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抗爭完都冇希望"},{"pid":"c36064797407485e1cb4ef41f696ca1f3f051e90","tid":724533,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:24:15.000Z","msg":"香港人係奴隸獸邊得閒出去抗爭"},{"pid":"ba97daa417637e446594c5480eb62a52e1a99a8e","tid":724533,"uid":52701,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:24:48.000Z","msg":"睇得到雨傘失敗之後，好多人都灰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36bc53d330938550ecadb492d216c3418b4b65bd","tid":724533,"uid":162272,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:25:08.000Z","msg":"現場好多人，去唔到睇直播嘅都成千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49a417188b6b064a5842b84171341c4ed334940","tid":724533,"uid":189048,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:30:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a23d1d60cfd3813c16b98c89ca2977b432e6b95","tid":724533,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:46:56.000Z","msg":"連登仔03年果時出左世未<br />\n我當年中五， 仲要係果日灣仔搞畢業聚餐<br />\n真係畢生難忘係個牧師著件濕曬既衫話完全行唔到跑過黎同我地講幾句祝福"},{"pid":"2bab07f020df1a8abed22e53f39aa60044a75904","tid":724533,"uid":1327,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T09:29:10.000Z","msg":"遊行無用論打擊左好多人<br />\n但d 人唔諗下<br />\n事實上每次超高人數的遊行都可以改變到政府<br />\n問題係幾多人出到黎"},{"pid":"82fcaf814e8c7ffdd1504cddd45c3ab310600773","tid":724533,"uid":22624,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"2bab07f020df1a8abed22e53f39aa60044a75904","tid":724533,"uid":1327,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T09:29:10.000Z","msg":"遊行無用論打擊左好多人<br />\n但d 人唔諗下<br />\n事實上每次超高人數的遊行都可以改變到政府<br />\n問題係幾多人出到黎"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:25:43.000Z","msg":"03年就係，而家個政府根本wfc<br />\n<br />\n雨革唔多人咩？魚蛋玩得唔夠大咩？最後政府又改變咗啲咩？"},{"pid":"a325ede765a4910031bc0b25e90c680e57ff40f1","tid":724533,"uid":29675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:29:54.000Z","msg":"<strong>民陣召集人葉志衍表示，估計有5萬人參與今年的七一遊行。警方則表示，遊行最高峰時有9800人。</strong><br />\n<br />\n葉志衍說，無論人數多少都感到滿意，有繼續舉行的價值。他又說，今年估算人數的工作比去年困難，因為沿途有市民加入，民陣無法確實說出人數多少，只透過不同街道的估算及遊行的時間作推算。他說，在維園草坪出發人數有數千至一萬，預計有幾萬人在中途加入。<br />\n<br />\n被問到七一遊行是否「行禮如儀」，葉志衍說，一件事要不斷去做，如集會遊行示威都做不到，談何更激烈的說法。<br />\n<br />\n葉志衍又說，民陣會與律師團隊研究，就警方發出不反對通知書，要求在維園草坪出發的做法，提出司法覆核。他指出，今日很多市民都中途加入，證明警方的說法不攻自破，呼籲警方日後要慎言。"},{"pid":"fdef5a946f2a8e28318e48b677d214c562271ea3","tid":724533,"uid":73310,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"ba97daa417637e446594c5480eb62a52e1a99a8e","tid":724533,"uid":52701,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:24:48.000Z","msg":"睇得到雨傘失敗之後，好多人都灰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:36:58.000Z","msg":"同時都睇清楚泛民班仆街係民建聯B隊黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e646831f53c053e92308c0551b2d08ad570d3364","tid":724533,"uid":54303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fdef5a946f2a8e28318e48b677d214c562271ea3","tid":724533,"uid":73310,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"ba97daa417637e446594c5480eb62a52e1a99a8e","tid":724533,"uid":52701,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:24:48.000Z","msg":"睇得到雨傘失敗之後，好多人都灰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:36:58.000Z","msg":"同時都睇清楚泛民班仆街係民建聯B隊黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:48:05.000Z","msg":"餓死班內鬼先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  要人課金呀拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"348d6afa1809f6c7ad7dbfc6e8721b1853038471","tid":724533,"uid":1327,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82fcaf814e8c7ffdd1504cddd45c3ab310600773","tid":724533,"uid":22624,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"2bab07f020df1a8abed22e53f39aa60044a75904","tid":724533,"uid":1327,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T09:29:10.000Z","msg":"遊行無用論打擊左好